               <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Aggressors</ENAMEX> don't control the rules. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Cynics</ENAMEX> reasoned that
