<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NATO</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">leaders</ENAMEX> simply refused to lose. Rather than accept the law of the
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">jungle</ENAMEX>, they overrode it. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clinton</ENAMEX> wagered, as he put it <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a week ago</TIMEX>, "that we
could raise the price to a point where it would no longer make any sense for
